<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>관리자 대시보드 - RANKING AI</title>
    <style>
        body { background: #0b0c0d; color: #fff; font-family: 'Pretendard', sans-serif; padding: 20px; margin: 0; }
        .header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; border-bottom: 2px solid #333; padding-bottom: 20px; margin-bottom: 30px; }
        .header h1 { margin: 0; color: #ff5722; font-size: 24px; }
        
        .dashboard { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 40px; }
        .card { background: #161718; padding: 20px; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid #333; text-align: center; }
        .card h3 { margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #aaa; font-size: 14px; }
        .card .number { font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold; color: #fff; margin: 0; }
        .card .number span { font-size: 16px; color: #777; }

        table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; background: #161718; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; }
        th, td { padding: 15px; text-align: left; border-bottom: 1px solid #333; }
        th { background: #222; color: #ff5722; font-weight: bold; }
        tr:hover { background: #1a1a1a; }
        
        .badge-admin { background: #ff5722; color: #000; padding: 3px 8px; border-radius: 5px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: bold; }
        .badge-user { background: #444; color: #fff; padding: 3px 8px; border-radius: 5px; font-size: 12px; }
        .btn-dm { background: #4caf50; color: #fff; border: none; padding: 6px 12px; border-radius: 5px; cursor: pointer; font-weight: bold; font-size: 12px; margin-right: 5px; }
        .btn-delete { background: #e53935; color: #fff; border: none; padding: 6px 12px; border-radius: 5px; cursor: pointer; font-weight: bold; font-size: 12px; }
        .action-cell { display: flex; gap: 5px; align-items: center; }

        .music-dropdown { background: #0f1011; }
        .music-item-li { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding: 10px 15px; background: #1c1d1e; margin-bottom: 5px; border-radius: 6px; border-left: 3px solid #ff5722; }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .header { flex-direction: column; gap: 15px; align-items: flex-start; }
            .dashboard { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 10px; } 
            .card { padding: 15px 10px; }
            .card .number { font-size: 24px; }
            
            table, thead, tbody, th, td, tr { display: block; }
            thead tr { display: none; } 
            
            tr { background: #161718; margin-bottom: 15px; border-radius: 10px; border: 1px solid #333; padding: 15px; }
            td { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; border: none; padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #222; }
            td:last-child { border-bottom: none; justify-content: flex-start; margin-top: 10px; }
            
            td::before { content: attr(data-label); font-weight: bold; color: #ff5722; font-size: 12px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-right: 15px; }
            td > div, td > span, td > strong { text-align: right; word-break: break-all; }
            .action-cell { width: 100%; justify-content: flex-end; }
            
            .music-dropdown { margin-top: -15px; border-top-left-radius: 0; border-top-right-radius: 0; }
            .music-dropdown td::before { display: none; }
            .music-dropdown td { display: block; padding: 5px 0 !important; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="header">
        <h1>👑 RANKING AI 종합 통제실</h1>
        <a href="/" style="color: #ff5722; text-decoration: underline; font-weight: bold; font-size: 14px;">← 메인으로 돌아가기</a>
    </div>

    <div style="display: flex; gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 30px; margin-top: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap;">
        <div style="flex: 1; min-width: 250px; background: #161718; border: 1px solid #333; padding: 25px; border-radius: 12px; text-align: center; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,229,255,0.1);">
            <div style="color: #aaa; font-size: 15px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 10px;">🟢 현재 실시간 접속자</div>
            <div style="font-size: 45px; color: #00e5ff; font-weight: 900; font-family: 'Pretendard', sans-serif;">
                <span id="live-user-count">0</span><span style="font-size:18px; color:#aaa; font-weight:bold;">명</span>
            </div>
            <div style="font-size: 11px; color: #555; margin-top: 5px;">(10초 단위 갱신)</div>
        </div>

        <div style="flex: 1; min-width: 250px; background: #161718; border: 1px solid #333; padding: 25px; border-radius: 12px; text-align: center; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255,87,34,0.1);">
            <div style="color: #aaa; font-size: 15px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 10px;">🎧 실시간 음악 재생 중</div>
            <div style="font-size: 45px; color: #ff5722; font-weight: 900; font-family: 'Pretendard', sans-serif;">
                <span id="live-play-count">0</span><span style="font-size:18px; color:#aaa; font-weight:bold;">명</span>
            </div>
            <div style="font-size: 11px; color: #555; margin-top: 5px;">(실시간 플레이어 구동 기준)</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        function updateLiveStats() {
            fetch('/api/admin/live-stats')
            .then(res => res.json())
            .then(data => {
                const userSpan = document.getElementById('live-user-count');
                const playSpan = document.getElementById('live-play-count');
                
                if (userSpan.innerText !== String(data.liveUsers)) {
                    userSpan.style.opacity = 0.5; setTimeout(() => userSpan.style.opacity = 1, 200);
                }
                if (playSpan.innerText !== String(data.playingUsers)) {
                    playSpan.style.opacity = 0.5; setTimeout(() => playSpan.style.opacity = 1, 200);
                }

                userSpan.innerText = data.liveUsers;
                playSpan.innerText = data.playingUsers;
            }).catch(e => {});
        }
        
        updateLiveStats();
        setInterval(updateLiveStats, 3000); 
    </script>

    <div class="dashboard">
        <div class="card" style="text-align: center;">
            <h3 style="color: #ff5722; font-size: 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid #333; padding-bottom: 10px;">👥 오늘 방문자 (총 <%= stats ? stats.dailyVisitors : 0 %>명)</h3>
            <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 10px 20px 0;">
                <div><span style="color: #ccc; font-size: 12px;">🔸 비회원</span><br><strong style="font-size: 24px; color: #00e5ff;"><%= stats ? (stats.guestVisitors || 0) : 0 %></strong></div>
                <div><span style="color: #ccc; font-size: 12px;">🔹 회원</span><br><strong style="font-size: 24px; color: #4caf50;"><%= stats ? (stats.memberVisitors || 0) : 0 %></strong></div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card" style="text-align: center;">
            <h3 style="color: #ff5722; font-size: 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid #333; padding-bottom: 10px;">🎧 오늘 재생수 (총 <%= stats ? stats.dailyPlays : 0 %>회)</h3>
            <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 10px 20px 0;">
                <div><span style="color: #ccc; font-size: 12px;">🔸 비회원</span><br><strong style="font-size: 24px; color: #00e5ff;"><%= stats ? (stats.guestPlays || 0) : 0 %></strong></div>
                <div><span style="color: #ccc; font-size: 12px;">🔹 회원</span><br><strong style="font-size: 24px; color: #4caf50;"><%= stats ? (stats.memberPlays || 0) : 0 %></strong></div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center;">
            <h3>전체 누적 방문자</h3>
            <p class="number"><%= stats ? stats.totalVisitors : 0 %> <span>명</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="card" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center;">
            <h3>전체 누적 재생수</h3>
            <p class="number"><%= stats ? stats.totalPlays : 0 %> <span>회</span></p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div style="background: #161718; padding: 20px; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid #333; margin-bottom: 30px; margin-top: 20px;">
        <h3 style="color: #ff5722; margin-top: 0; font-size: 16px;">🌍 오늘 국가별 페이지 조회수(PV)</h3>
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap;">
            <% if (typeof countryStats !== 'undefined' && countryStats.length > 0) { %>
                <% countryStats.forEach(c => { %>
                    <span style="background: #222; padding: 8px 15px; border-radius: 20px; font-weight: bold; border: 1px solid #444; font-size: 14px;">
                        <%= c._id %> : <span style="color: #00e5ff;"><%= c.count %>회</span>
                    </span>
                <% }) %>
            <% } else { %>
                <span style="color: #777; font-size: 14px;">아직 수집된 국가 데이터가 없습니다.</span>
            <% } %>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div style="display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        <button class="period-btn" onclick="loadChartData('daily', this)" style="padding: 8px 25px; border-radius: 20px; border: 1px solid #ff5722; background: #ff5722; color: #fff; font-weight: bold; cursor: pointer; transition: 0.3s;">일간 (최근 7일)</button>
        <button class="period-btn" onclick="loadChartData('monthly', this)" style="padding: 8px 25px; border-radius: 20px; border: 1px solid #444; background: #222; color: #aaa; font-weight: bold; cursor: pointer; transition: 0.3s;">월간 (최근 12개월)</button>
        <button class="period-btn" onclick="loadChartData('yearly', this)" style="padding: 8px 25px; border-radius: 20px; border: 1px solid #444; background: #222; color: #aaa; font-weight: bold; cursor: pointer; transition: 0.3s;">연간 (전체)</button>
    </div>

    <div style="background: #1a1b1c; padding: 20px; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid #ff5722; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px; transition: 0.3s;">
        <h3 id="dwell-time-title" style="color: #ccc; margin-top: 0; font-size: 16px;">🕒 [일간] 사이트 총 체류 시간</h3>
        <p id="total-dwell-time" style="font-size: 32px; color: #ffb300; font-weight: 900; margin: 10px 0 0 0;">
            <%= typeof todayPlayTime !== 'undefined' ? todayPlayTime : '0초' %>
        </p>
    </div>

    <div style="background: #1a1b1c; padding: 20px; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid #333; margin-bottom: 40px;">
        <h3 style="color: #fff; margin-top: 0; text-align: center;">📈 접속 & 재생 변동 추이</h3>
        <canvas id="trendChart" style="max-height: 300px;"></canvas>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js"></script>
    <script>
        let myChart; 

        function renderChart(labels, visitorsData, playsData) {
            const ctx = document.getElementById('trendChart').getContext('2d');
            
            if (myChart) {
                myChart.destroy(); // 새로 그릴 때 이전 그래프를 깔끔하게 날려줌
            }

            myChart = new Chart(ctx, {
                type: 'line',
                data: {
                    labels: labels,
                    datasets: [
                        {
                            label: '방문자 수 (명)',
                            data: visitorsData,
                            borderColor: '#4caf50',
                            backgroundColor: 'rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.1)',
                            borderWidth: 2,
                            tension: 0.4,
                            fill: true
                        },
                        {
                            label: '재생 수 (회)',
                            data: playsData,
                            borderColor: '#ff5722',
                            backgroundColor: 'rgba(255, 87, 34, 0.1)',
                            borderWidth: 2,
                            tension: 0.4,
                            fill: true
                        }
                    ]
                },
                options: {
                    responsive: true,
                    maintainAspectRatio: false,
                    plugins: {
                        legend: { labels: { color: '#fff', font: { family: 'Pretendard' } } }
                    },
                    scales: {
                        x: { ticks: { color: '#aaa' }, grid: { color: '#333' } },
                        y: { ticks: { color: '#aaa', beginAtZero: true }, grid: { color: '#333' } }
                    }
                }
            });
        }

        // 🌟 버튼 클릭 시 서버 자판기에서 데이터를 뽑아오는 마법 함수
        function loadChartData(period, btnElement) {
            document.querySelectorAll('.period-btn').forEach(btn => {
                btn.style.background = '#222';
                btn.style.color = '#aaa';
                btn.style.borderColor = '#444';
            });
            if(btnElement) {
                btnElement.style.background = '#ff5722';
                btnElement.style.color = '#fff';
                btnElement.style.borderColor = '#ff5722';
            }

            const titleMap = {
                'daily': '🕒 [일간] 사이트 총 체류 시간',
                'monthly': '🕒 [월간] 사이트 총 체류 시간',
                'yearly': '🕒 [연간] 사이트 총 체류 시간'
            };
            document.getElementById('dwell-time-title').innerText = titleMap[period];

            fetch('/api/admin/chart-data?period=' + period)
            .then(res => res.json())
            .then(data => {
                if(data.error) return;
                document.getElementById('total-dwell-time').innerText = data.displayTime || '0초';
                renderChart(data.labels, data.visitorsData, data.playsData);
            })
            .catch(err => console.error("차트 로딩 에러:", err));
        }

        // 🌟 페이지 처음 열렸을 때 기본 데이터 렌더링
        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            const initialLabels = <%- typeof chartDates !== 'undefined' ? JSON.stringify(chartDates) : '[]' %>;
            const initialVisitors = <%- typeof chartVisitors !== 'undefined' ? JSON.stringify(chartVisitors) : '[]' %>;
            const initialPlays = <%- typeof chartPlays !== 'undefined' ? JSON.stringify(chartPlays) : '[]' %>;
            
            renderChart(initialLabels, initialVisitors, initialPlays);
        });
    </script>
    <h2 style="margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 18px;">👥 회원 가입 목록 (총 <%= users ? users.length : 0 %>명)</h2>
    <table>
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th>가입일</th>
                <th>아이디(닉네임)</th>
                <th>업로드 수 🌟</th>
                <th>오늘 접속</th>
                <th>총 접속</th>
                <th>등급</th>
                <th>관리(쪽지/탈퇴)</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            <% if(users && users.length > 0) { %>
                <% users.forEach(user => { %>
                    <tr>
                        <td data-label="가입일"><%= user.createdAt ? new Date(user.createdAt).toLocaleDateString() : '날짜 없음' %></td>
                        <td data-label="닉네임"><strong><%= user.username %></strong> <%= user.nickname ? `(${user.nickname})` : '' %></td>
                        
                        <td data-label="업로드 수">
                            <span style="color:#00e5ff; font-weight:bold; text-decoration:underline; cursor:pointer;" onclick="toggleMusicList('<%= user.username %>')">
                                🎧 <%= user.musicCount %>곡 보기
                            </span>
                        </td>

                        <td data-label="오늘 접속" style="color: #ffb300; font-weight: bold;"><%= user.todayLogins || 0 %>회</td>
                        <td data-label="총 접속" style="color: #4caf50; font-weight: bold;"><%= user.totalLogins || 0 %>회</td>

                        <td data-label="등급">
                            <% if(user.role === 'admin') { %>
                                <span class="badge-admin">관리자</span>
                            <% } else { %>
                                <span class="badge-user">일반회원</span>
                            <% } %>
                        </td>
                        <td data-label="관리" class="action-cell">
                            <% if(user.role !== 'admin') { %>
                                <button type="button" class="btn-dm" onclick="sendMsg('<%= user.username %>')">💌 쪽지</button>
                                <form action="/admin/delete-user" method="POST" style="margin:0;" onsubmit="return confirm('<%= user.username %> 회원을 탈퇴시키겠습니까?');">
                                    <input type="hidden" name="userId" value="<%= user._id %>">
                                    <button type="submit" class="btn-delete">탈퇴</button>
                                </form>
                            <% } else { %>
                                <span style="color: #777; font-size: 12px; font-weight: bold;">최고 관리자</span>
                            <% } %>
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                    <tr id="music-list-<%= user.username %>" class="music-dropdown" style="display: none;">
                        <td colspan="7" style="padding: 15px; border: 1px dashed #444;"> <% if (user.uploadedMusic && user.uploadedMusic.length > 0) { %>
                                <ul style="list-style:none; padding:0; margin:0;">
                                    <% user.uploadedMusic.forEach(music => { %>
                                        <li class="music-item-li">
                                            <div style="font-size:13px; flex: 1;">
                                                <strong style="color:#fff;"><%= music.name %></strong> - <%= music.artist %> 
                                                <span style="color:#ff5722; font-size:11px; margin-left:8px;">(조회수: <%= music.views || 0 %>)</span>
                                            </div>
                                            <form action="/admin/delete-music-only/<%= music._id %>" method="POST" style="margin:0;" onsubmit="return confirm('이 곡을 강제 삭제하시겠습니까?');">
                                                <button type="submit" class="btn-delete" style="padding:4px 8px; font-size:11px; margin-left: 10px;">곡 삭제</button>
                                            </form>
                                        </li>
                                    <% }) %>
                                </ul>
                            <% } else { %>
                                <div style="text-align:center; color:#777; font-size:13px; padding:10px;">업로드한 곡이 없습니다.</div>
                            <% } %>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                <% }) %>
            <% } else { %>
                <tr><td colspan="7" style="text-align:center; padding: 30px;">가입한 유저가 없습니다.</td></tr>
            <% } %>
        </tbody>
    </table>

    <form id="msgForm" action="/admin/send-message" method="POST" style="display:none;">
        <input type="hidden" name="userId" id="msgUserId">
        <input type="hidden" name="text" id="msgText">
    </form>

    <script>
        function sendMsg(userId) {
            const text = prompt(`[${userId}] 님에게 보낼 쪽지 내용을 입력하세요:\n(예: 경고 1회입니다. / 이벤트 당첨을 축하합니다!)`);
            if (text && text.trim() !== "") {
                document.getElementById('msgUserId').value = userId;
                document.getElementById('msgText').value = text;
                document.getElementById('msgForm').submit();
            }
        }

        function toggleMusicList(username) {
            const row = document.getElementById('music-list-' + username);
            if (row.style.display === 'none') {
                row.style.display = window.innerWidth <= 768 ? 'block' : 'table-row';
            } else {
                row.style.display = 'none';
            }
        }
    </script>

    <div style="margin: 40px 0; padding: 25px; background: #161718; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid #333; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);">
        <h2 style="color: #ff5722; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 5px;">📢 메인 화면 팝업 공지 설정</h2>
        <p style="color: #aaa; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 20px;">사이트 메인 화면에 띄울 중요한 공지사항이나 추천 콘텐츠를 설정하세요.</p>
        
        <form action="/admin/popup" method="POST">
            <div style="margin-bottom: 15px;">
                <label style="font-weight: bold; color: #fff; display: block; margin-bottom: 8px;">팝업 제목</label>
                <input type="text" name="title" placeholder="예: 🔥 이번 주 강력 추천 AI K-POP!" required style="width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 12px; background: #0f1011; color: #fff; border: 1px solid #444; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 16px;">
            </div>

<div style="margin-bottom: 15px;">
                <label style="color:#ff5722; font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; display:block; margin-bottom:8px;">🎵 팝업 추천곡 고유 ID (선택 사항)</label>
                <input type="text" name="recommendedTrackId" value="<%= typeof popup !== 'undefined' && popup ? popup.recommendedTrackId : '' %>" placeholder="예: 661b2c3... (비워두면 차트 1위 곡 자동 재생)" style="width:100%; box-sizing:border-box; background:#0f1011; border:1px solid #444; color:#fff; padding:12px; border-radius:6px; font-size:14px;">
                <p style="color:#888; font-size:12px; margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:0;">* 팁: 메인 차트에서 추천할 곡의 <strong>'수정'</strong> 버튼을 누르면 주소창 맨 끝에 나오는 영문/숫자가 바로 곡 ID입니다.</p>
            </div>
            <div style="margin-bottom: 15px;">
                <label style="font-weight: bold; color: #fff; display: block; margin-bottom: 8px;">팝업 내용 (HTML 태그 사용 가능)</label>
                <textarea name="content" rows="4" placeholder="예: 라디오 기능을 켜고 24시간 끊김 없이 들어보세요! <br><br> <a href='/radio' style='color:#ff5722;'>[라디오 바로가기]</a>" required style="width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 12px; background: #0f1011; color: #fff; border: 1px solid #444; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 14px;"></textarea>
            </div>
            
            <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; background: #1a1b1c; padding: 15px; border-radius: 6px; border: 1px solid #333; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 15px;">
                <label style="font-weight: bold; cursor: pointer; color: #ff5722; display: flex; align-items: center; font-size: 15px;">
                    <input type="checkbox" name="isActive" style="width: 20px; height: 20px; margin-right: 10px; cursor: pointer;"> 
                    🚨 이 팝업을 메인 화면에 즉시 띄우기
                </label>
                <button type="submit" style="background: #ff5722; color: #fff; padding: 12px 25px; border: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 15px; cursor: pointer; transition: 0.3s;">
                    💾 팝업 저장 및 적용
                </button>
